KYZ017-210900-
Christian-
Including the city of Hopkinsville
614 PM CDT Sun Jul 20 2025

...HEAT ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 8 PM CDT /9 PM EDT/ THIS
EVENING...

.TONIGHT...Partly cloudy. Lows in the mid 70s. Southwest winds
around 5 mph.
.MONDAY...Mostly sunny. A slight chance of showers and
thunderstorms in the morning, then a chance of showers and
thunderstorms in the afternoon. Humid with highs in the lower
90s. West winds 5 to 10 mph. Chance of rain 40 percent.
.MONDAY NIGHT...Mostly cloudy in the evening, then becoming
partly cloudy. Humid with lows in the mid 70s. Northwest winds
around 5 mph in the evening, becoming light and variable.
.TUESDAY...Mostly sunny. Humid with highs in the lower 90s. South
winds around 5 mph, becoming northeast around 5 mph in the
afternoon.
.TUESDAY NIGHT...Partly cloudy in the evening, then becoming
mostly clear. Lows in the lower 70s. East winds around 5 mph in
