.TONIGHT...Mostly cloudy. A chance of showers and thunderstorms
this evening, then showers and thunderstorms likely after
midnight. Some thunderstorms may produce heavy rainfall. Lows in
the lower 70s. Northwest winds around 5 mph, becoming east around
5 mph after midnight. Chance of rain 70 percent.
.MONDAY...Mostly cloudy in the morning, then becoming partly
sunny. A chance of showers and thunderstorms. Some thunderstorms
may produce heavy rainfall. Highs in the upper 80s. East winds
around 5 mph, becoming north around 5 mph in the afternoon.
Chance of rain 40 percent.
